Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total waiting time to the SW-AE Assign Reviewers following SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the subsequent occurrence of Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs within the same variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-AE Assign Reviewers and activity SW-Reviewer Agreed for cases where activity SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Minimum time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Agreed across all process variants containing both activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers when immediately followed by another SW-AE Assign Reviewers activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-AE Assign Reviewers compared to the time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time between consecutive executions of SW-AE Assign Reviewers before reaching SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Cycle Time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers measured from its first occurrence to the final reviewer agreement (SW-Reviewer Agreed) in multi-attempt variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that bypass immediate reviewer agreement
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers to be followed by a reviewer outcome (SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
